{"tid":1803056,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者指黃色經濟圈屬營商手法　施永青則認為是干預行為","createTime":"2019-12-30T02:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T08:43:12.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c8eff2a28e7ca07d9f54e011fde16767c78dcc94","tid":1803056,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"因應反修例運動，有市民倡議「黃色經濟圈」，港大經濟及工商管理學院助理講師阮穎嫻表示，從營商角度看，商戶表態支持反修例運動吸引市民消費，作為營商手法無可厚非，認為是一種以政治包裝的商戶行為，和主張環保的產品相類似。<br />\n<br />\n阮穎嫻在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，「黃色經濟圈」能否持續下去，取決於消費者取態能否持續，亦要看政府會否有其他刺激市民的行為。<br />\n<br />\n中原集團主席兼總裁施永青則認為，「黃色經濟圈」對經濟未必有好處。他說旗下不只一間公司收到電話，要求停止在電視台播出廣告，否則會有嚴重後果，這些行為干預沒參與抵制的人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500106-20191230.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500106-20191230.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkcQbtkMcGro9tlpYeKwNq%2B0%3D&h=d869dacb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500106-20191230.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b18ea579\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500106-20191230.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d9259eb26629bcc7a709b3171e30afdf97630c6f","tid":1803056,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcbab0eb17f51254b2ab4275b228e27032f8c05","tid":1803056,"uid":59910,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"咁罷買日貨買國貨講左幾多年？"},{"pid":"7879a441ae63c0c2c90b536c6637b44968006179","tid":1803056,"uid":34553,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"干預<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"